### See how Emma uses tech to manage her diabetes
Using technology to manage your diabetes is more than just gadgets. Emma uses
apps to help with her Type 2 diabetes.
### Peter shares what tech works for his type 1 diabetes
Peter has been living with diabetes for over 6 decades. In his story, he
explains how technology has changed and what he's learnt along the way.
Whether you're new to diabetes technology or if you've been using it for a
long time, there's a place for you on our forum.
